  <p class="section-intro">At a $125K–$145K price point, usability failure is not an annoyance — it is a brand-defining event. Owners who cannot operate the climate system, hitching procedure, or HMI within 15 minutes of first use will generate social media content that disproportionately damages the brand. Usability testing is mandatory, not optional.</p>

