    <div style="background:#1e293b;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;border-top:3px solid #f6ad55;text-align:center"><div style="font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px">🛡️</div><div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#f6ad55;margin-bottom:4px">Error Tolerance</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#a0aec0;line-height:1.5">HV interlock, hitch checklist on HMI, colour-coded connections — all error-tolerance decisions</div></div>
