<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ §24 QUALITY SYSTEMS ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="panel" id="panel-ls-24">
  <div class="eyebrow-sm" style="margin-bottom:16px">§24 · Quality Systems</div>
  <p class="section-intro">Quality is embedded at every phase gate — it is not a post-design activity. The Quality Plan spans supplier quality, in-process controls, end-of-line testing, field failure workflow, reliability engineering, and continuous improvement.</p>

