<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ §27 PROGRAM MANAGEMENT CONTROLS ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="panel" id="panel-ls-27">
  <div class="eyebrow-sm" style="margin-bottom:16px">§27 · Program Management Controls</div>
  <p class="section-intro">Program management controls are the governance mechanisms that ensure the L1 program delivers on scope, schedule, and budget. This section defines RACI decision rights, risk burndown, issue management, change freeze dates, and gate review templates.</p>

