<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ §31 SUSTAINABILITY & EOL ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="panel" id="panel-ls-31">
  <div class="eyebrow-sm" style="margin-bottom:16px">§31 · Sustainability &amp; End-of-Life (EOL) Strategy</div>
  <p class="section-intro">An electric trailer with an unrecycled LFP battery is not the environmental improvement it claims to be. Regulatory pressure is also accelerating: EU Battery Regulation 2023/1542 mandates battery passport tracking. This section defines the full lifecycle sustainability strategy.</p>

  <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap">
