═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="panel" id="panel-0" data-panel-idx="0">
  <p class="section-intro">Before any DSM is built, the three candidate architectures must be clearly defined. Each concept represents a fundamentally different answer to the same question: <em>how should aerodynamics, structure, and systems be integrated?</em> That choice determines every WBS seam downstream.</p>

  <!-- Concept selector tabs -->
