  </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     PANEL 2 — CONCEPT SELECTION / GATE 1
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="panel" id="panel-2" data-panel-idx="2">
  <p class="section-intro">Gate 1 decision: all three criteria — aerodynamic performance, cost/feasibility, and coupling structure — are weighed simultaneously. DSM makes coupling a first-class input rather than an afterthought discovered in execution.</p>

  <table class="cmp-table" style="margin-bottom:20px">
