</div>



<div class="panel" id="panel-3" data-panel-idx="3">
  <p class="section-intro">Now that the aeroshell architecture is locked, the Level 2 DSM maps the <strong style="color:#f7fafc">subsystems</strong> of that specific architecture. Tightly coupled subsystems form clusters — and those cluster boundaries become the WBS control account seams.</p>

  <div class="grid2">
    <div>
