          <div class="label">WHAT THIS UNLOCKS</div>
          <p style="margin-bottom:8px">Once WBS is baselined you have named subsystems with owners. Requirements can now be <em>allocated</em> to those subsystems — no owner, no interface boundary, no test jurisdiction without this.</p>
