      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#a0aec0;line-height:1.65">Status advances gate by gate. All rows must reach CLOSED before Gate 5 (commercial launch). A row that stays OPEN past Gate 3 is a programme risk item — it means either a requirement has no test or a test has no requirement.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- RTM table -->
  <div class="box" style="margin-bottom:20px;padding:0;overflow:hidden">
    <div style="background:#1a202c;padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #2d3748">
      <div class="eyebrow-sm" style="margin-bottom:0">RTM snapshot — Lightship L1 (excerpt, 12 of 47 rows)</div>
    </div>
    <!-- Header -->
