      <div style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:36px;color:#f6ad55">47</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#718096;margin-top:4px">Total PRS requirements</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#a0aec0;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5">RTM skeleton opened at Gate 1. All 47 IDs assigned before a single design drawing exists.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="box" style="text-align:center;border-top:3px solid #63b3ed">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:36px;color:#63b3ed">47</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#718096;margin-top:4px">FRS allocations (Gate 3)</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#a0aec0;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5">Every PRS requirement decomposed to ≥1 FRS subsystem requirement. RTM fully LINKED at CDR.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="box" style="text-align:center;border-top:3px solid #68d391">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:36px;color:#68d391">47</div>
