      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#a0aec0;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5">All 47 test cases executed and passed. RTM 100% CLOSED. Gate 5 launch approved.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="detail-box mt20" style="border-color:#4a5568">
    <div class="eyebrow-sm">Complete sequence — from DSM to closed RTM</div>
    <div class="flow-chain">
      <div class="flow-box done"><div class="flow-box-label">DSM L1</div><div class="flow-box-sub">Coupling eval</div></div>
      <div class="flow-connector">→</div>
      <div class="flow-box done"><div class="flow-box-label">Concept</div><div class="flow-box-sub">Gate 1</div></div>
      <div class="flow-connector">→</div>
      <div class="flow-box done"><div class="flow-box-label">DSM L2</div><div class="flow-box-sub">Clusters</div></div>
      <div class="flow-connector">→</div>
