    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#a0aec0;line-height:1.7;margin-top:4px">Each step is a prerequisite for the next. You cannot correctly place WBS seams without DSM clusters. You cannot allocate FRS requirements without WBS control accounts. You cannot prove V&V coverage without an RTM that started at the PRS. Skipping or reordering any step produces rework — the only question is whether you do it intentionally now or accidentally later.</p>
