  <div id="budget-view-earned" style="display:none">
    <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom:18px">Earned Value Management tracks whether you are getting the work you paid for. It compares three curves — planned, actual cost, and earned value — to give an objective, schedule- and cost-independent view of programme health.</p>
    <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:18px">
      <div class="box">
